{
  "stem": "9723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uh, the people in-- in this army were-- were Poles who were originally, most of them, expelled from Poland by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, Russians knew they were going to retake Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wanted to make sure that the military and the government was communist-oriented rather than right-wing-oriented.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they wanted to make sure that the Polish army was Russian sponsored and not otherwise.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they formed a Russian arm-- a Polish army under Russian auspices.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The uniforms were Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, many officers were Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Uh, but also, many were Russian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I guess there were not enough qualified people [INAUDIBLE]-- Did they know you were Jewish?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they did not know that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Um, I felt much more anti-Semitism after the liberation than any time, uh-- well, of course, I can't speak about German occupation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But before the war, uh, in comparison, uh, it was very uh, mild.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember after we were liberated in Lodz, I was walking on the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was short time after the liberation, perhaps uh-- or perhaps it was after we came back from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So must have been about two months after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was walking down the street and I was attacked by a-- a bunch of kids.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Older-- most of them were older than me, perhaps a year, two years, three years older, teenagers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Several of them, saying oh, you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're not supposed to be alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they beat me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's something I couldn't understand, just why-- why would they do that?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 12, 12 and a half.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So uh, when I tried to join the army, first of all, I told them I was an orphan.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no place to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
